description: Chicago Cupcake has created the most divine cakes you have ever tasted and will leave you wanting more.The artisan cupcakes have three distinct layers: the frosting, the cake, and the crust.The silky smooth Italian buttercream frosting was created to provide a light, fluffy, and decadent experience. The flavor combinations are carefully paired with the different cakes in order to fully accentuate the flavor experience.Crafted in small batches, the dairy infusion process makes the cakes so unbelievable moist and flavorful, you won't be able to stop eating them. Created with 100% all natural ingredients and never any additives, preservatives, artificial flavors or coloring.Finally, the crusts have been specifically chosen based on how they compliment the sinfully delicious desserts.
name: Chicago Cupcake
